<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AWS DevOps Infrastructure</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e3a8a,#0f766e);
min-height:100vh;
color:#fff;
}

.header{
padding:30px 8%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
}

.logo{
font-size:30px;
font-weight:700;
color:#38bdf8;
}

.hero{
padding:60px 8%;
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr;
gap:50px;
align-items:center;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:52px;
line-height:1.2;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero h1 span{
color:#22c55e;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
line-height:1.8;
color:#d1d5db;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.button{
display:inline-block;
padding:15px 35px;
background:#22c55e;
color:#fff;
text-decoration:none;
border-radius:8px;
font-weight:600;
}

.card{
background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
padding:35px;
border-radius:18px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
}

.card h2{
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
gap:18px;
}

.item{
background:#fff;
color:#111827;
padding:20px;
border-radius:12px;
text-align:center;
}

.item h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
color:#2563eb;
}

.tech{
padding:70px 8%;
}

.tech h2{
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:45px;
font-size:36px;
}

.tech-grid{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));
gap:25px;
}

.tech-card{
background:white;
color:#111827;
padding:25px;
border-radius:15px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
transition:.3s;
}

.tech-card:hover{
transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.tech-card img{
width:70px;
height:70px;
margin-bottom:15px;
}

.footer{
margin-top:60px;
padding:25px;
text-align:center;
background:#020617;
color:#cbd5e1;
}

.status{
margin-top:20px;
padding:18px;
background:#dcfce7;
color:#166534;
border-radius:10px;
font-weight:bold;
font-size:18px;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.hero{
grid-template-columns:1fr;
text-align:center;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<header class="header">

<div class="logo">
AWS DevOps
</div>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div>

<h1>
Ubuntu EC2 <span>Successfully Deployed</span>
</h1>

<p>

This server has been provisioned automatically using
Terraform Infrastructure as Code (IaC).

Nginx has been installed successfully and is serving this
website from an Ubuntu EC2 instance hosted on Amazon Web Services.

</p>

<a href="#" class="button">
Infrastructure Running
</a>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>Deployment Summary</h2>

<div class="grid">

<div class="item">
<h3>Cloud</h3>
AWS EC2
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>OS</h3>
Ubuntu 24.04
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Web Server</h3>
Nginx
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>IaC</h3>
Terraform
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Language</h3>
Python Certified
</div>

<div class="item">
<h3>Platform</h3>
Linux
</div>

</div>

<div class="status">

Deployment Status : SUCCESS

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="tech">

<h2>Technology Stack</h2>

<div class="tech-grid">

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/amazonwebservices/amazonwebservices-original-wordmark.svg">
<h3>AWS Cloud</h3>
<p>Elastic Compute Cloud</p>
</div>

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/ubuntu/ubuntu-plain.svg">
<h3>Ubuntu</h3>
<p>Ubuntu 24.04 LTS</p>
</div>

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/nginx/nginx-original.svg">
<h3>Nginx</h3>
<p>High Performance Web Server</p>
</div>

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/terraform/terraform-original.svg">
<h3>Terraform</h3>
<p>Infrastructure as Code</p>
</div>

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg">
<h3>Python</h3>
<p>Python Certified</p>
</div>

<div class="tech-card">
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/linux/linux-original.svg">
<h3>Linux</h3>
<p>System Administration</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<footer class="footer">

<h2>AWS Mumbai Region (ap-south-1)</h2>

<p>

Provisioned using Terraform • Ubuntu • Nginx • Linux • Python

</p>

<br>

<p>

© 2026 DevOps Infrastructure Demonstration

</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>